# Orion-Sentinel-DataAICore - Profiles Reference
#
# This file documents the available Docker Compose profiles.
# Profiles control which services are started.
#
# Usage:
#   ./scripts/orionctl up <profile> [profile...]
#   docker compose --profile <profile> up -d
#

# ==============================================================================
# AVAILABLE PROFILES
# ==============================================================================

# Profile: nextcloud
# -----------------
# Services: PostgreSQL, Redis, Nextcloud, Nextcloud Cron
# Purpose: Self-hosted cloud file sync and collaboration
# Access: http://${HOST_IP}:8080
# Dependencies: None
#
# Usage:
#   ./scripts/orionctl up nextcloud

# Profile: websearch
# ------------------
# Services: SearXNG
# Purpose: Privacy-focused meta-search engine
# Access: http://${HOST_IP}:8888
# Dependencies: None
# Note: Phase 1 - No local document indexing (no Meilisearch/Tika)
#
# Usage:
#   ./scripts/orionctl up websearch

# Profile: llm
# ------------
# Services: Ollama, Open WebUI
# Purpose: Local LLM inference with ChatGPT-like interface
# Access: http://${HOST_IP}:3000 (Open WebUI)
# Dependencies: None
# Note: Requires pulling a model after startup
#
# Usage:
#   ./scripts/orionctl up llm
#   ./scripts/pull-model.sh llama3.2:3b

# Profile: public-nextcloud
# -------------------------
# Services: Caddy reverse proxy
# Purpose: Expose ONLY Nextcloud to the internet
# Access: https://cloud.${ORION_DOMAIN}
# Dependencies: nextcloud profile must also be enabled
# Requirements:
#   - Domain name with DNS A record
#   - Router port forwarding (443 → server)
#   - ORION_DOMAIN set in .env
#
# Usage:
#   ./scripts/orionctl up nextcloud public-nextcloud

# ==============================================================================
# BUNDLES (SHORTCUTS)
# ==============================================================================

# Bundle: core
# ------------
# Profiles: nextcloud + websearch + llm
# Purpose: All primary services for daily use
#
# Usage:
#   ./scripts/orionctl up core

# ==============================================================================
# RECOMMENDED CONFIGURATIONS
# ==============================================================================

# Minimal (just cloud storage):
#   ./scripts/orionctl up nextcloud

# Cloud + Search:
#   ./scripts/orionctl up nextcloud websearch

# Cloud + AI:
#   ./scripts/orionctl up nextcloud llm

# Full Stack (recommended):
#   ./scripts/orionctl up core

# Public Nextcloud (internet-accessible):
#   ./scripts/orionctl up nextcloud public-nextcloud
#   (Other services remain local-only)
